                            <comment id="10083" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Wed, 14 Jan 2004 08:20:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Only tried this with ojdbc14.jar from Oracle 9i yet (it&apos;s brand-new) - will adapt this to be compatible with classes12.zip as you suggested (reading the constants via reflection). Will also use context class loader. Thanks for the report!&lt;/p&gt;

